 -->\n<p><a href=\"https://fdnyhns.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/HigherEducationScholarshipApplication.pdf\" data-type=\"attachment\" data-id=\"166\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click here to download our Higher Education Scholarship Application</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">High School Scholarship Test</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Commencing 8:30 a.m.<br>Location: <strong>To Be Announced</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>High School Scholarship applications will be available after September from the Scholarship Chairman William Meade <a href=\"mailto:wm519@msn.com\">wm519@msn.com</a>, 718-335-9685, or PO Box 525, Maspeth, NY 11378.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Completed applications must be returned to William Meade one week before the test date.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://fdnyhns.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/HighSchoolScholarshipApplication.pdf\" data-type=\"attachment\" data-id=\"163\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click here to download our High School Scholarship Application</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">Mail your completed application to:\nWilliam Meade, PO Box 525, Maspeth, NY 11378</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">High School Scholarships Awards</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our High School Scholarship awards are: two awards for four years to a catholic high school will be $1,500.00 per year for four years. The Fordham Prep award will stay the same. The Vincent A. McCarthy Scholarship Award for $2,000.00 and the Captain Larry Monachelli Award for $1,500.00 are one time cash awards. You will NOT be required to attend a Catholic high school, but you will be required to take the High School Scholarship Test. If you have any questions, contact us from our web site link or an E-mail: <a href=\"mailto:holyname@fdnyholynamesociety.com\">holyname@fdnyholynamesociety.com</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Scholarships','','publish','closed','closed','','scholarships','','','2024-03-07 22:20:20','2024-03-07 22:20:20','',0,'https://fdny-hns.flywheelstaging.com/?page_id=115',0,'page','',0),(116,2,'2024-03-07 23:42:09','2024-03-07 23:42:09','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Spring 2023 Schedule - COMING SOON</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->','Meetings','','publish','closed','closed','','meetings','','','2024-03-07 23:48:08','2024-03-07 23:48:08','',0,'https://fdny-hns.flywheelstaging.com/?page_id=116',0,'page','',0),(117,2,'2024-03-07 23:41:54','2024-03-07 23:41:54','<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">JUBILEE 2024 - 99<sup>th</sup> Communion Mass &amp; Breakfast</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>In Memory of Our Fallen Firefighters</em><br>Sunday, April 14th, 2024</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://www.saintpatrickscathedral.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">St. Patrick\'s Cathedral</a> - mass at 10:00am</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Communion breakfast to follow immediately following the mass at the<br>New York Hilton Hotel<br>Avenue of the America\'s &amp; 53rd Street</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Honorees</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>John Corcora