>Members are invited to attend in their Class A Uniform<br>11:45 am at<br>Saint Barnabas Church<br>409 East 241st Street<br>Bronx, NY 10470</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Dominican Sisters Annual Autumn Festival</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Date to be announced</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Dominican Sisters of Blauvelt, N.Y. will sponsor their annual Autumn Festival. Join us for a day of fun, food, children\'s activities, games of chance, raffles, flea market, and entertainment.<br>Parking is available on the grounds located at 496 Western Highway, Blauvelt, N.Y. <br>Any questions, contact: <a href=\"mailto:pford@opblauvelt.org\">pford@opblauvelt.org</a> or <a href=\"mailto:jschaaf@opblauvelt.org\">jschaaf@opblauvelt.org</a>.<br>Visit the <a href=\"http://www.opblauvelt.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Domincan Sisters of Blauvet</a> website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Marriage Encounter Weekend</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your marriage &amp; your family are precious gifts. Don\'t you deserve a Marriage Encounter Weekend to enrich &amp; deepen the joys a couple shares? Come &amp; explore together your hopes &amp; dreams for your marriage. Your invited to bring back the romance &amp; rediscover your love for each other. The Marriage Encounter Weekend is a time to focus on communication with your spouse &amp; allow time to explore important areas of life together without every day stresses &amp; distractions. Every couple deserves it!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more info on the World wide Marriage Encounter Weekends visit: <a href=\"http://www.wwme.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">www.wwme.org</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Events','','publish','closed','closed','','events','','','2024-03-08 00:26:13','2024-03-08 00:26:13','',0,'https://fdny-hns.flywheelstaging.com/?page_id=117',0,'page','',0),(118,2,'2024-03-07 23:42:30','2024-03-07 23:42:30','','Membership','','publish','closed','closed','','membership','','','2024-03-07 23:42:31','2024-03-07 23:42:31','',0,'https://fdny-hns.flywheelstaging.com/?page_id=118',0,'page','',0),(119,2,'2024-03-07 23:42:46','2024-03-07 23:42:46','','Sponsors','','publish','closed','closed','','sponsors','','','2024-03-07 23:42:49','2024-03-07 23:42:49','',0,'https://fdny-hns.flywheelstaging.com/?page_id=119',0,'page','',0),(120,2,'2024-03-07 21:26:53','2024-03-07 21:26:53','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Most Recent Newsletter: <strong>Spring 2020</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->','Newsletters','','inherit','closed','closed','','113-revision-v1','','','2024-03-07 21:26:53','2024-03-07 21:26:53','',113,'https://fdny-hns.flywheelstaging.com/?p=120',0,'revision','',0),(121,2,'2024-03-07 21:27:15','2024-03-07 21:27:15','','HNSNewsletterSpring2020','','inherit','open','closed','','hnsnewsletterspring2020','','','2024-03-07 21:27:15','2024-03-07 21:27:15','',0,'http://fdny-hns.flywheelstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/HNSNewsletterSpring2020.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(122,2,'2024-03-07 21:27:56','2024-03-07 21:27:56','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Most Recent Newsletter: <strong><a href=\"https://fdnyhns.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/HNSNewsletterSpring2020.pdf\" data-type=\"attachment\" data-id=\"121\">Spring 2020</a></strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list 